main event: Three round objects were observed moving in a circular course overhead in Berlin, Germany on January 22, 1953.
interesting points: The objects were described as small bright lights that flew in a circular motion without making any sound.,The observation lasted for about 5 minutes.,The objects moved from east to west across a clear sky.,The witness believed the objects might represent advanced technology, possibly of extraterrestrial origin.,The report is part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings.
